data.text:
``update chiaki_production.chi_product_feeds
set is_show = 1
where code in (
	select code from chi_product where (store_id = 1 or store_id is null)
	union 
	(	select chi_product_variant_code.product_variant_code 
		from chi_product 
		inner join chi_product_variant_code 
		on chi_product.id = chi_product_variant_code.product_id
		where (chi_product.store_id = 1 or chi_product.store_id is null)
	)
) and id > 0;``
